text: Try Sutrisno (, born 15 November 1935) is an Indonesian politician. He is the sixth vice president. He held office from 11 March 1993 to 10 March 1998. ==Other websites== *Profile at TokohIndonesia.com (In Indonesian) *Info on Tanjung Priok Incident |- |- Category:1935 births Category:Living people Category:Vice presidents of Indonesia
